      • createCreateEntity

        public CreateEntity createCreateEntity(ItemIdentifier itemIdentifier,
                              String itemTypeId,
                              Collection<CardChangeSet> newCards,
                              Collection<SecurityAccessPermission> accessPermissions,
                              Collection<SecurityGrantPermission> grantPermissions,
                              String securityPermissionsSignpost,
                              Collection<PrimaryPropertyIdentifier> primaryPropertyIdentifiers)
        Creates and returns a CreateEntity command.
        Parameters:
        itemIdentifier - An ItemIdentifier for the created Entity, generated using an IdentifierFactory.
        itemTypeId - A String containing the identifier of the ItemType for the created Entity, retrieved from the Schema.
        newCards - CardChangeSets containing information for the cards of the created Entity, generated using a CardChangeSetFactory.
        accessPermissions - SecurityAccessPermissions for the created Entity.
        grantPermissions - SecurityGrantPermissions for the created Entity.
        securityPermissionsSignpost - A String indicating whom to contact to obtain increased permissions on the created Entity.
        primaryPropertyIdentifiers - PrimaryPropertyIdentifiers for the created Entity.
        Returns:
        See above.

      • createCreateLink

        public CreateLink createCreateLink(ItemIdentifier itemIdentifier,
                          String linkTypeId,
                          ItemIdentifierAndOptionalVersion fromEntityIdentifier,

                          LinkDirection linkDirection,
                          String linkStrengthId,
                          Collection<CardChangeSet> newCards,

                          Collection<SecurityGrantPermission> grantPermissions,
                          String securityPermissionsSignpost,
                          Collection<PrimaryPropertyIdentifier> primaryPropertyIdentifiers)
        Creates and returns a CreateLink command.
        Parameters:
        itemIdentifier - An ItemIdentifier for the created Link, generated using an IdentifierFactory.
        linkTypeId - A String containing the identifier of the ItemType for the created Link, retrieved from the Schema.
        fromEntityIdentifier - The ItemIdentifierAndOptionalVersion of the Entity at the "from" end of the created Link.
        toEntityIdentifier - The ItemIdentifierAndOptionalVersion of the Entity at the "to" end of the created Link.
        linkDirection - A LinkDirection value for the created Link.
        linkStrengthId - A String containing the identifier of the LinkStrength for the created Link, retrieved from the Schema.
        newCards - CardChangeSets containing information for the cards of the created Link, generated using a CardChangeSetFactory.
        accessPermissions - SecurityAccessPermissions for the created Link.
        grantPermissions - SecurityGrantPermissions for the created Link.
        securityPermissionsSignpost - A String indicating whom to contact to obtain increased permissions on the created Link.
        primaryPropertyIdentifiers - PrimaryPropertyIdentifiers for the created Link.
        Returns:
        See above.
